description:
Instead of trusting God in times of trouble, Abraham often succumbed to his fear, choosing his own way over God’s and endangering his own family in the process. Does God’s plans have to change when we disobey Him? Can we trust that His ways are higher than ours? Follow Abraham in his adventures to Egypt, and take heart in the reality of our unchanging and loving God. Watch Francois DuPlessis present the results of Abraham's departure from God's plan instead of remaining in the promised land.
